sub_title: International Tourism and Travel Industry Student at the NHTV
summary: I am an organised, creative and motivated student at the NHTV. Currently I am studying International Tourism and Travel Industry with the wish to acquire knowledge and experience with and within the tourism industry. Thriving within my education, my ambition is to start up an enterprise in the future with which I can make my contribution to the society.
